{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Funciones","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Functions","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT#referencia_de_xslt.2fxpath\">Referencia de XSLT y XPath</a></b>: <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">Elementos XSLT</a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/EXSLT\">Funciones EXSLT</a>, <ahref=\" es=\"\" docs=\"\" web=\"\" xpath=\"\" funciones\"=\"\">XPath:Funciones, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath:Ejes</a>\n</ahref=\"></div> A continuación se presenta una lista ordenada de las funciones core de&nbsp;<font color=\"#0066cc\">XPath</font> y agregados específicos de <font color=\"#0066cc\">XSLT </font>a XPath, incluyendo una descripción, sintaxis, un listado de argumentos, tipo de resultado, referencia apopiada a W3C y el estado actual de soporte en el motor&nbsp;<font color=\"#0066cc\">Gecko</font>. para más información sobre el uso de las funciones de XPath/XSLT, por favor vea la página <a href=\"/en-US/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/For_Further_Reading\" title=\"en/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/For_Further_Reading\"><u><font color=\"#0066cc\">Para más información</font></u></a>.<p></p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/boolean\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/boolean\">boolean()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/ceiling\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/ceiling\">ceiling()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/choose\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/choose\">choose()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/concat\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/concat\">concat()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/contains\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/contains\">contains()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/count\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/count\">count()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/current\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/current\">current()</a> <em>Específico de XSLT</em></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/document\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/document\">document()</a> <em>Específico de XSLT</em></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/element-available\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/element-available\">element-available()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/false\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/false\">false()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/floor\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/floor\">floor()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/format-number\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/format-number\">format-number()</a> <em>Específico de XSLT</em></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/function-available\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/function-available\">function-available()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/generate-id\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/generate-id\">generate-id()</a> <em>Específico de XSLT</em></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/id\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/id\">id()</a> <em>(Parcialmente soportado)</em></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/key\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/key\">key()</a> <em>Específico de XSLT</em></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/lang\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/lang\">lang()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/last\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/last\">last()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/local-name\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/local-name\">local-name()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/name\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/name\">name()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/namespace-uri\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/namespace-uri\">namespace-uri()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/normalize-space\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/normalize-space\">normalize-space()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/not\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/not\">not()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/number\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/number\">number()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/position\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/position\">position()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/round\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/round\">round()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/starts-with\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/starts-with\">starts-with()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/string\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/string\">string()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/string-length\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/string-length\">string-length()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/substring\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/substring\">substring()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/substring-after\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/substring-after\">substring-after()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/substring-before\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/substring-before\">substring-before()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/sum\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/sum\">sum()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/system-property\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/system-property\">system-property()</a> <em>Específico de XSLT</em></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/translate\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/translate\">translate()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/true\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/true\">true()</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/XPath/Functions/unparsed-entity-url\" title=\"en/XPath/Functions/unparsed-entity-url\">unparsed-entity-url()</a> <em>Específico de XSLT (no soportado)</em></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Functions","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Fonctions","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Functions","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"